How to Listen

     * Apple Podcasts
     * Google Podcasts
     * Pandora

   You can listen to Serial in many places: right here on our site, on
   Apple Podcasts, Google Podcasts, and on Pandora.

   You can also find the podcast on Stitcher, RadioPublic or the
   podcatcher of your choice. Don’t know how to get a podcast? Learn more
   here.

