All Episodes

   Please listen to the episodes in order.

   Episode 01

A Bar Fight Walks into the Justice Center

   A young woman at a bar is slapped on the butt. So why’s she the one in
   jail?
   Play Season Three: Episode 01: A Bar Fight Walks into the Justice
   Center

   Episode 02

You’ve Got Some Gauls

   When a judge believes he knows you better than you know yourself.
   Play Season Three: Episode 02: You’ve Got Some Gauls

   Episode 03

Misdemeanor, Meet Mr. Lawsuit

   ​The smell of raw marijuana + acting nervous + hands in pockets = ?
   Play Season Three: Episode 03: Misdemeanor, Meet Mr. Lawsuit

   Episode 04

A Bird in Jail Is Worth Two on the Street

   What happens when the right evidence points to the wrong man?
   Play Season Three: Episode 04: A Bird in Jail Is Worth Two on the
   Street

   Episode 05

Pleas Baby Pleas

   Don’t tell the judges, but the prosecutors have the most power in the
   building.
   Play Season Three: Episode 05: Pleas Baby Pleas

   Episode 06

You in the Red Shirt

   Life after you put a cop in jail.
   Play Season Three: Episode 06: You in the Red Shirt

   Episode 07

The Snowball Effect

   If you listen closely to the trash-talking, you start to get the
   message.
   Play Season Three: Episode 07: The Snowball Effect

   Episode 08

A Madman’s Vacation

   A teenager decides to cooperate.
   Play Season Three: Episode 08: A Madman’s Vacation

   Episode 09

Some Time When Everything Has Changed

   The state of Ohio decides where Joshua belongs.
   Play Season Three: Episode 09: Some Time When Everything Has Changed

About Season Three

   Serial is heading back to court. This time, in Cleveland. A year inside
   a typical American courthouse. This season we tell you the
   extraordinary stories of ordinary cases. One courthouse, told week by
   week.
